=== EVENT_PIRATE_BASE ===
# id: 8
# title: Pirate Base
# chinese_title: 海盗基地
# category: PirateEncounter
# mode: starmap

Long-range scans reveal a hidden pirate outpost nestled in an asteroid field. Its hangars glow with stolen cargo.

* [Raid the outpost]
  ~ combat_reward(3, 40)
  突袭 (tūxí) — raid
* [Sneak past while their patrols are away]
  ~ gain_fuel(2)
  潜行 (qiánxíng) — sneak
* [Hail them and offer to trade]
  ~ gain_item("Pirate Star Chart")
  贸易 (màoyì) — trade
